ddl_create: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS oasisreport (schemalocation TEXT, PRIMARY KEY (schemalocation));

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS messageheader (source TEXT, version TEXT, timedate TEXT, oasisreport_schemalocation TEXT, FOREIGN KEY (oasisreport_schemalocation) REFERENCES oasisreport(schemalocation), PRIMARY KEY (source, version, timedate));
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS messagepayload (id TEXT, oasisreport_schemalocation TEXT, FOREIGN KEY (oasisreport_schemalocation) REFERENCES oasisreport(schemalocation), PRIMARY KEY (id));
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS rto (name TEXT, messagepayload_id TEXT, FOREIGN KEY (messagepayload_id) REFERENCES messagepayload(id), PRIMARY KEY (name));
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS report_item (id TEXT, rto_name TEXT, FOREIGN KEY (rto_name) REFERENCES rto(name), PRIMARY KEY (id));

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS report_header (mkt_type TEXT, interval TEXT, report TEXT, uom TEXT, tz TEXT, sec_per_interval INTEGER, system TEXT, report_item_id TEXT, FOREIGN KEY (report_item_id) REFERENCES report_item(id), PRIMARY KEY (mkt_type, interval, report, uom, tz, sec_per_interval, system));

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS report_data (direction TEXT, to_baa TEXT, data_item TEXT, tie_name TEXT, baa_grp_id TEXT, value INTEGER, interval_end_gmt TEXT, interval_start_gmt TEXT, from_baa TEXT, id TEXT, report_item_id TEXT, FOREIGN KEY (report_item_id) REFERENCES report_item(id), PRIMARY KEY (direction, to_baa, data_item, tie_name, baa_grp_id, value, interval_end_gmt, interval_start_gmt, from_baa, id));
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS disclaimer_item (disclaimer TEXT, rto_name TEXT, FOREIGN KEY (rto_name) REFERENCES rto(name), PRIMARY KEY (disclaimer));
